            </svg>
            <span data-i18n="fee_t">Merksatz</span>
          </div>
          <p class="muted" data-i18n="fee_p">
            Profit = Verkauf − Kauf − (Marketplace Fee) − (Royalties) − (Gas/Network Fees).
          </p>
        </div>

